Name: ggs_signing_id_tooltip
English:
To distribute your title outside of the Mac App Store macOS requires that your
package is codesigned. Please provide the signing identity that you wish to use
here: this should be a Developer ID Application identity and should be present
in your Mac's login keychain certificates. Signing identities can be easily created
in Xcode->Preferences->Accounts->Team->View Details->Developer ID
Application->Create. Signing identities will be matched so the default value
should be sufficient if you are only the member of one development team.
Translation: 要将标题发布到Mac App Store macOS之外，需要对您的\ n包进行代码签名。请在此处提供您希望使用的签名身份\：这应该是开发人员ID应用程序的身份，并且应该存在于\ n Mac的登录钥匙串证书中。可以轻松创建签名身份\ n在Xcode->首选项->帐户->团队->查看详细信息->开发人员ID \ n应用程序->创建中。签名身份将匹配，因此如果您只是一个开发团队的成员，则默认值\ n就足够了。

Translation: 高抗锯齿算法，最好只用在单色输出的画面中

Translation: 优先采用自动微调算法而非字体自带的微调机制 \n 这选项将被"禁用自动微调"和"禁用微调"选项覆盖

Translation: 稍微扭曲字形以优化网格对齐 \n 这功能依赖"自动微调"和"普通"微调模式

Name: Project_Changes_Message
English: Changes detected in project directory '{0}'. Would you like to reload the resources, or save?\n\nWARNING: Save will only update the resources files that are currently held in memory, and therefore may not restore some deleted or edited files
Translation: 项目目录'{0}'中监测到更改。你想要重新加载项目，还是保存呢？n\n警告：保存只会更新当前内存中的资源文件，因此可能不会恢复一些删除或编辑过的文件。

Comment: message box title when the project directory has detected changes

Name: Project_Deletions_Message
